"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></nav><main class=\"pt-20\"><div class=\"min-h-screen\"><section class=\"relative py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-charcoal overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0\"><img alt=\"Art In The Alley murals\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-20\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fart-in-alley-murals.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fart-in-alley-murals.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fart-in-alley-murals.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fart-in-alley-murals.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fart-in-alley-murals.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fart-in-alley-murals.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fart-in-alley-murals.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fart-in-alley-murals.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fart-in-alley-murals.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6\"><div class=\"h-px w-16 bg-gold/40\"></div><div class=\"w-3 h-3 rotate-45 border border-gold/60\"></div><div class=\"h-px w-16 bg-gold/40\"></div></div><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl tracking-wide text-cream\">Art In The Alley</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto text-cream/70\">Where creativity meets community in the heart of downtown.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-cream\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-brush text-gold\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m11 10 3 3\"></path><path d=\"M6.5 21A3.5 3.5 0 1 0 3 17.5a2.62 2.62 0 0 1-.708 1.792A1 1 0 0 0 3 21z\"></path><path d=\"M9.969 17.031 21.378 5.624a1 1 0 0 0-3.002-3.002L6.967 14.031\"></path></svg></div><div><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl text-charcoal\">Community Art Event</h2><p class=\"text-charcoal/50 text-sm\">Live painting, music &amp; Art Deco creativity</p></div></div><p class=\"text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-6\">A vibrant community art event featuring local artists, live painting, music, and Art Deco-inspired creativity. Art In The Alley transforms downtown spaces into open-air galleries celebrating the intersection of art and architecture.</p><p class=\"text-charcoal/70 leading-relaxed mb-8\">Whether you&#x27;re an artist, collector, or simply curious, Art In The Alley welcomes everyone to experience the creative energy of the Palm Beaches&#x27; Art Deco heritage brought to life.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 p-6 bg-cream rounded-2xl\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/60\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin text-gold shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><span class=\"text-sm\">Downtown Lake Worth Beach</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/60\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar text-gold shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm\">Check events for dates</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-charcoal/60\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail text-gold shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg><a href=\"mailto:Art@ArtDecoPB.org?subject=Art In The Alley\" class=\"text-sm text-gold hover:text-copper transition-colors\">Get involved</a></div></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-8\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3]\"><img alt=\"Art installation on fence\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fart-in-alley-fence-photo.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fart-in-alley-fence-photo.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fart-in-alley-fence-photo.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3]\"><img alt=\"Art In The Alley event flyer\" loading